title: Mad Games Tycoon v0.150324A
description:
Information: Old save games can not be loaded.

- Now you can select the game size. (B, B+, A, AA, AAA)
- Bank has been added.
- Great games increase the market share of platforms.
- It now comes a message if you have not enough money.
- You can now build some objects in the hallway.
- New research added (Game Size).
- Added Chinese language.
- Different languages have been updated.
- Balance: Fans are easier to satisfy.
- Balance: It is now harder to get a high rating game.
- Bug removed: Development costs of subsidiaries have been calculated incorrectly.
- Bug removed: There were errors if the goodwill of subsidiaries was too high.
- Bug removed: (Completed Game Screen) Sound & technology points were displayed incorrectly
